@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@candidateId = 1

### 查询第三方能力
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/capabilities

### 测试 Ollama
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/capabilities/ollama/test

### 测试 SearXNG
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/capabilities/searxng/test

### 保存 SearXNG 配置
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/capabilities/searxng
Content-Type: application/json

{"endpoint":"http://127.0.0.1:8088","model":"","authenticationType":"NONE","credential":"","enabled":true,"defaultProvider":true,"fallbackProvider":false}

### 发现候选采集源
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sources/search-discovery
Content-Type: application/json

{"topic":"人工智能治理","language":"zh-CN","count":5,"sourceType":"HTML_LIST","qualityLevel":"权威"}

### 查询候选
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sources/discovery-candidates

### 验证候选
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sources/discovery-candidates/{{candidateId}}/validate

### 导入候选
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sources/discovery-candidates/{{candidateId}}/import

### 查询调用日志
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/capabilities/calls?limit=20
